# Page-Specific Styles

This directory is for page-specific complete CSS files.

## When to use this directory:
- Landing pages with unique designs
- Marketing pages with custom layouts
- Pages that need specific CSS not used elsewhere

## Structure:
Each page CSS file should import necessary base styles:

```css
@import "tailwindcss";
@import "../../base/_variables.css";
@import "../../base/_base.css";
@import "../../base/_animations.css";
@import "../../base/_headings.css";
@import "../../fonts/index.css";

/* Page-specific styles */
```

## Example:
- `welcome.css` - Homepage styles
- `about.css` - About page styles
- `pricing.css` - Pricing page styles
